entries.femaleVariant: Come on!
Ass in gear, V!
Are they here yet?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="私が… 気づかないとでも思ったのか？" t="Did you think I wouldn't know it was taken from me?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="これで、もう誰のことも許す必要はない" t="You shall never have to forgive me for anything again." b="" a=""/>
I wish... I wish to put the hotel on lockdown.
Guys! Focus! The safe!
Relic intact?
"Bioshard integrity – one hundred percent." Guessin' that's a yes.
Good. Let's go!
We're in.
Which don't solve our problem, T.
I fuckin' know our problem's still there!
What the fuck just happened in there?
Just lost T…
They approach from the landing pad.
Saburo Arasaka?!
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="外してくれ" t="Leave us." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="アラサカ様、まだボディチェックが終わっていません" t="Arasaka-sama, I still haven't done a full sweep." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="私の息子だ" t="This is my son." b="" a=""/>
Saburo Arasaka has been murdered.
Code red initiated.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="そもそも俺のことを気にしたことなんかないだろう" t="Actually, I don't think of you at all. Ever." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="あんたの問題点はそこだ。世界は自分中心に回ってると思ってる。傲慢だよ" t="You see, that's your problem. You think the world revolves around you. Arrogant." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ヨリノブ…" t="Yorinobu." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="どうしてここへ？ 直々に俺に屈辱を味わせ、立場を思い知らせるためにか？" t="Why did you come? To humiliate me? To personally see to it that your son knows his place?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="「出る杭は打たれる」とよく言うだろう" t="\"The nail that protrudes from the wall gets hammered...\" " b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="自分の言葉じゃ何も言えないのか？" t="Couldn't think of anything original to say?" b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="jpn" o="貴様こそ、自分が何をしようとしたかわかっているのか？ 私たちの功績を野蛮人に渡すなど… 私たちの未来を…" t="And do you think it \"original\" to sell our greatest achievement to Westerners – our future to these... barbarians?!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="「俺たちの未来」？ 俺たち？ なんかの間違いだろう。あんたは自分のことしか考えてない。そしてこの会社のことしか" t="Our future? Ours?! You are mistaken. You've only ever cared about yourself… and your sick schemes." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="いつかこのような日が来ることはわかっていた… 貴様は、ついに超えてはならない一線を超えたのだ" t="I knew this day would come. That sooner or later your impudence would cross the line." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="これまでお前の愚行には目をつぶってきた。だが、それもここまでだ。この裏切りだけは決して許せん" t="There is much for which I could forgive you, but for treason – no." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="貴様の母親が生きていなくてよかった。息子の不甲斐ない姿を目の当たりにして、心を痛めずに済んだのだからな…" t="I'm just glad your mother didn't live to see this. The heart should break but once." b="" a=""/>
May I ask why?
Attention! Code Red has been initiated throughout Konpeki Plaza. Please remain in your rooms and follow all instructions given by staff.
Jack in your personal and make us rich!
On it.
[Jack in]
Your turn, Bug.
Gimme two…
How much longer, T?!
There. Under the floor.
Lemme look to this, eh?
Is tha--... Is that Adam Smasher?!
We wait...
Fuck are they talking about?
Bug, who we got incoming?
Nuh-uh, no fucking way...! This isn't happening...!
Oh, shit...
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="何の騒ぎです？" t="What happened?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="誰かが… 誰かが父に毒を盛った" t="Someone... someone poisoned my father." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="毒を？" t="Poisoned?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="タケムラ、お前の仕事は何だ？" t="What is your job, Takemura?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="何の話です？" t="I don't follow." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="単純な質問だ。答えろ" t="It's a simple question. Answer it." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="アラサカ家の家長を守ることです" t="To protect the head of the Arasaka family." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="今後はもっとしっかり責任を果たすよう望んでいるぞ…" t="I do sincerely hope you'll do a better job of executing your duties from now on…" b="" a=""/>
I been made…! Aaarrghhh!
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="そうだ" t="It seems so." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ヨリノブさん… しかし…" t="Yorinobu-san... I doubt..." b="" a=""/>
Hurry up, V!
Got no time for this!
[Squeeze through]
[Get out]
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="お許しください、アラサカ様。決して失望はさせません" t="Forgive me, Arasaka-sama. I shall not disappoint." b="" a=""/>
His own fuckin' pops...
Gotta get us out of here, T.
Bug, need you to get us out of here. Now!
Where's Yorinobu?
Where's Yorinobu?!
I don't... I don't know! I've lost camlinks!
Whole building's being put on lockdown!
Window – now!
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Chica" b="" a=", wait up!"/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="Mano" b="" a=", wait up!"/>

entries.femaleVariant: What?
Old man Arasaka – he never left... His AVs gotta be on the roof still, right?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="首を突っ込まないでくれって言っただろう" t="I thought I told you not to meddle in my affairs." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="例のモノを回収しましょうか…?" t="Of course. Should I retrieve what we came here to…?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="私がやる。行ってくれ" t="I will handle it. You may go." b="" a=""/>
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Bien pensado." b="" a=" Old man Arasaka's AV should still be parked on the roof."/>
Think it's synthetic?
Check out that weird-ass lizard!
Look, V, another fuckin' iguana!
Nah, no way, our guy had a saggier neck, many, many folds.
Saburo-fuckin'- Arasaka's dead. Feels weird to even say it.
Nah, they could afford a real one, 'thout a doubt.
That ain't no lizard, it's an iguana, ya twit. Know 'cause I've seen one before.
Shit, you're right. Think it's the same one?
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Pinche Dios Santo bendito!" t="Jesus fucking Christ!" b="" a=""/>
And make it quick!
We got winged visitors... Bug...?
Can't say I like this…
What is he, a fuckin' sorcerer?
Some kinda dead zone's my guess – have him back in a sec. And you do your damn job!
Bodyguard?
Worse. Night City legend. Bleak motherfuckin' one, too. What's the play?
Un-fucking-believable… Saburo Arasaka.
Know what this means?! Security's gonna swarm the place any second!
No, no, no, no – not now...!
Forget it. It'll be AI-guided, fully automated. You can forget about hacking, much less piloting the damn thing.
Figures. Still, let's head up to the roof anyway. Might find somethin' else.
Forget it. It'll be AI-guided, fully automated. You can forget about hacking, much less piloting the damn thing.
Shit. Yorinobu's penthouse bound!
Fuck him! Open the safe!
Done!
Preem!
What now?
Fat pillar – try that!
No! Inside it! Now!
Bingo, got somethin' ejectin! C'mere, V!
Look around for a switch.
Fuck, too late! Yorinobu's about to walk in – find cover!
Releasing the lock!
Should see a ladder... Ladder... Oh fuck…
Dunno who. But staff's abuzz, all two hundred on their feet, can't keep still.
Almost got it…
Where?!
Bug!
Fuck!
Oh my god, we're so fucked!
Gimme a sec!
We don't have a sec!
OK, got somethin'!
Fuck...!
Fuckin' major leagues! Happy now, Jackie?!
<mothertongue l="mex" m="chica!" b="Come on, " a=""/>
The emperor?
Sure as shit better'n bein' the son of Raúl Welles.
Why, what's the rush?
Sig on Yorinobu's gone dark!
Lemme think for a sec, OK?
Yorinobu... just offed Saburo!
What?!
We ain't dyin' – not today!
Huh... not bad bein' heir to the Arasaka empire.
You fuckin' kiddin'?!
Looks like Yorinobu left us a parting gift!
Ain't much, but it'll have to do!
<mothertongue l="mex" m="¡Chica!" b="" a=" Don't do this to me!"/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="¡Ese!" b="" a=" Don't do this to me!"/>

entries.femaleVariant: Whoa...
Hurry up! Yorinobu could be back any second!
You gonked!? You wanna die here?! Hide!
V, there's time for thinkin', time for gettin' the fuck out! Let's go!
Shush. Doubt this cubby's soundproof.
Yet another asslickin' legend…
Oh fuck…
Sshh.
Wooo, close…
Too close. If he'da sniffed us out…
<mothertongue l="mex" m="cállate." b="But he didn't. Now " a=""/>
Fuuuck me…
That's that. We done for.
[Turn on]
